    "date": "2023-08-10T21:06:06Z",
    "text": "Driver Reimbursement Increase for Veteran Equity Act or the DRIVE Act\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to adjust the mileage rate for beneficiary travel to or from a VA facility in relation to vocational rehabilitation, required counseling, or for the purpose of examination, treatment, or care. Such rate must be adjusted to be at least equal to the mileage reimbursement rate for vehicles that are privately owned by government employees on official business."
